TODOApplication is an open-source ToDo and reminder application which provides a user with simplicity as well as productivity. It comes with a clean materialistic design.

Its a simple ToDo list manager meant to be the base platform for some ideas that are centered around making reminders and todo lists.

It was built by Pronoy Mukherjee and its provided at no cost.

Alongside being able to make to do lists, there is the option for the addition of reminders

Features

*Its a simple ToDo list application 

*Ability to add, delete and sort todo lists and add reminders

*Material design

*Ability to add categories and priority levels

*Focused on design

*Open-source

*More features coming soon


With the light, intuitive and easy to use features of TODOApplicationÂ  it is the todo list and reminder you can use on the Go.
